    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "These ruins… they feel heavier than the others.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Because everything here already ended.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Ended? Before what?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Before you even arrived.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "So… this is where we use Past Perfect?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Yes. To show what happened before something else in the past.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Like: She had left before he arrived.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. 'had' + past participle.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "They had known each other before the fall.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "The past behind the past.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "And what happens if I use only Past Simple?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Then you blur the order. These walls hate that.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Okay, better not upset the ruins.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
